Summary: KHR_materials_pbrSpecularGloss is an archived glTF extension deprecated for new files but still supported for loading old files.

KHR_materials_pbrSpecularGloss is an archived glTF extension. This means that it is deprecated and not recommended for new files. However, it is still supported for loading old files.
