Document: GLTFSpecGloss  
Path: godot/classes/class_gltfspecgloss.rst  
Summary: Properties for configuring material diffuse, gloss, and specular settings in GLTFSpecGloss.  

diffuse_factor (Color): The reflected diffuse factor of the material. Default: Color(1, 1, 1, 1). Set via set_diffuse_factor(Color), get via get_diffuse_factor().  
diffuse_img (Image): The diffuse texture. Set via set_diffuse_img(Image), get via get_diffuse_img().  
gloss_factor (float): The glossiness or smoothness of the material. Default: 1.0. Set via set_gloss_factor(float), get via get_gloss_factor().  
spec_gloss_img (Image): The specular-glossiness texture. Set via set_spec_gloss_img(Image), get via get_spec_gloss_img().  
specular_factor (Color): The specular RGB color of the material. The alpha channel is unused. Default: Color(1, 1, 1, 1). Set via set_specular_factor(Color), get via get_specular_factor().